        <p class="lede-p"><strong>Koala AI is the cheapest serious AI writer on the market.</strong> It is also a word-credit system that burns faster than the marketing implies. After 30 days inside Essentials, Starter, and Pro — plus interviews with 9 paying customers — here is the honest 2026 verdict, the real total cost at 30 articles per month, and the workflows where Koala genuinely wins.</p>

