          <p>Every Koala subscriber we interviewed underestimated their word usage by <strong>2–3×</strong>. The "150,000 words" marketing on Essentials does not account for regenerations, KoalaChat usage, system prompts, or article retries. Budget for Starter ($25/mo) minimum if you publish more than 10 articles per month.</p>
